cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or the bundled anonymized data, please cite it as below."
title: "2inspire-neurokit-pipeline: Hexoskin ECG + RSP cardiorespiratory feature extraction with NeuroKit2"
abstract: >-
  A self-contained pipeline that extracts heart-rate-variability and respiratory
  features from raw Hexoskin signals (single-lead ECG at 256 Hz and dual-channel
  respiration at 128 Hz) using NeuroKit2. Built for the 2Inspire study of
  physiology during live piano performance (PI: Muneesh Tewari).
type: software
authors:
